  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Basics in Anti-Corruption Education (BACE)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Anti-corruption curriculum developed, with lesson notes for teachers.

2.     6-part animation series developed to go with the curriculum

3.     10 master trainers trained in the use of the BACE curriculum

4.     Stakeholder buy-in secured from at least 200 stakeholders in the education sector.

5.     1500 students pilot the BACE curriculum in 2 schools.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Development of 6-part national anti-corruption curriculum
&#xB7;         Pre-test draft curriculum in 2 schools (Urban Accra and peri-urban Accra)
&#xB7;         National Curriculum Review Meeting
&#xB7;         Production of animation series.
&#xB7;         Train teachers of pilot schools
&#xB7;         Pilot BACE curriculum in 2 schools for 1 term
&#xB7;         Printing of final curriculum and duplication of animation series.
&#xB7;         National advocacy with GES and other stakeholders.
&#x2022;Media advocacy</narrative>
  </description>
